    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-05-14T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-05-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="595"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d595">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 731.51/58.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-05-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 14, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The protocol was ratified by the Congress May 13.</p>
                <p>The Minister for Foreign Affairs requests the further friendly offices of the
                    Government of the United States with the French Government to assist in securing
                    settlements with French claimants out of court as favorable as justice will
                    allow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Northcott</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
